most_popular.title: Most Popular
most_popular.description: The people have spoken! See the most-watched movies now on Tubi!

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

469586.title: Hard Target
469586.description: The line between the hunted and the hunter becomes blurred when one man finds himself fighting a group that hunts other men for blood sport.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

516859.title: The Last Witch Hunter
516859.description: A fearless, immortal witch hunter ends up in a ferocious battle with supernatural enemies as he fights to save the human race from evil.

571078.title: Obsessed
571078.description: A happily married businessman finds his life in shambles after a woman pursues him relentlessly, putting his wife in a dangerous predicament.

573585.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
573585.description: When a young man receives his grandfather’s distress signal from a remote island, he heads off with his stepfather and a helicopter tour team.

593866.title: Baby Boy
593866.description: The classic John Singleton film about a 20-year-old in South Central L.A. who loves like a man but isn’t stepping up in real life as a grown adult.

607105.title: American Me
607105.description: Edward James Olmos stars as a powerful Folsom State prisoner who returns to society after running the game behind bars for 18 years.

607952.title: True Lies
607952.description: A deadly and talented spy for the government hides his dangerous day job from his family, but his secret heroics take a toll on his marriage.

609721.title: The Karate Kid
609721.description: Jaden Smith stars in the 2010 reboot of the iconic franchise, this time as a young arrival in China who learns self-defense from a karate master.

610572.title: Goodfellas
610572.description: Based on a true story, a young man rises up the ranks of a mob family over several years, dabbling in drugs, heists and murders along the way.

616516.title: Bring It On: All or Nothing
616516.description: When a popular cheerleader moves from her posh neighborhood to a working-class one, she soon finds herself at odds with her new classmates.

628970.title: Hellboy II: The Golden Army
628970.description: Hellboy and his crew of paranormal outcasts face off with forces of darkness in this imaginative adventure from visionary director Guillermo del Toro.

630919.title: Major Payne
630919.description: In peacetime, a major with a lust for war is discharged from the Marine Corps and reduced to training a group of misfit ROTC cadets at a prep school.

630921.title: The Last House on the Left
630921.description: After their daughter is raped and left for dead, a couple exact bloody revenge on the attackers who have unknowingly taken shelter at their home.

639561.title: The Waterboy
639561.description: A socially awkward but well-meaning water boy's violent temper tantrums inspire a football coach to train him as his team’s defensive tackle.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

647479.title: Sister Act 2: Back in the Habit
647479.description: A Las Vegas showgirl-turned-singing nun becomes a run-down Catholic school’s only hope of reviving its music program and keeping its doors open.

652270.title: The Goonies
652270.description: A pair of brothers hope to save their house by following a treasure map and taking their friends along on a subterranean sea adventure.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

663215.title: How High
663215.description: Silas and Jamal are two slackers who beat the odds and get accepted to Harvard, where they turn the school upside down with their pursuit of parties.

664191.title: Double Take
664191.description: An investment banker on the run swipes the passport of a petty thief, thus swapping identities, in this comic urban take on the Prince and the Pauper.

667422.title: Pacific Rim
667422.description: With alien invaders rising from the sea, a washed-up former pilot and an untested trainee use massive robots to combat the apocalyptic threat.

672287.title: The Angry Birds Movie
672287.description: When mysterious green piggies visit an island populated by flightless birds, it's up to three unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to.

675608.title: Saban's Power Rangers
675608.description: Five ordinary teenagers must team together to become something extraordinary in order to save the world from being obliterated by an alien threat.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

701398.title: The Minute You Wake Up Dead
701398.description: In this noir thriller, a stockbroker romances a waitress as multiple murders shock a small Southern town. Someone’s getting rich. But who?

711197.title: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
711197.description: A comically penned love letter to 1990’s urban films that follows the eventful life of a teen boy and his crew after he moves into his father’s ‘hood.

720947.title: Little Man
720947.description: After a stolen diamond gets stashed in the home of a husband and wife, a pint-sized jewel thief poses as the world's ugliest baby to get it back.

100000221.title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
100000221.description: A mysterious map sends the Smurfs on a thrilling race through a forbidden forest filled with magical creatures to find a forgotten hamlet.

100000302.title: Real Steel
100000302.description: In a near future where human boxers have been replaced by robots, a struggling ex-boxer and his estranged son reunite while training a robot fighter.

100001222.title: Rosewood
100001222.description: In this film inspired by true events, a mob attacks the Black residents of Rosewood, Florida after a false accusation incites racist violence.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001725.title: Mindcage
100001725.description: Two detectives must strike a deal with a brilliant serial killer on death row who turned his victims into art exhibits when a copycat killer strikes.

100001935.title: The Predator
100001935.description: When a young boy accidentally sparks a battle with genetically-enhanced aliens, a ragtag crew of ex-Marines bands together to save the human race.

100001992.title: Illegal Tender
100001992.description: When his family's shadowy past comes back to haunt them, a college student learns the dark source of their wealth and fights off their enemies.

100002047.title: Bring It On
100002047.description: With national championships fast approaching, the new cheerleading captain discovers that their winning routines were stolen from a rival squad.

100002087.title: King Kong
100002087.description: A devious producer leads his crew to an ominous island full of deadly creatures, where a giant ape becomes captivated by the film’s leading lady.

100002110.title: Evil Among Us: The Golden State Killer
100002110.description: To the world, Joe DeAngelo was a devoted family man, reliable friend & proud police officer. But secretly, he was a serial rapist & murderer who haunted California for over 40 years.

100002155.title: A Body to Kill For
100002155.description: Growing up in Philadelphia, China enjoys a life of privilege until a handsome suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that changes her forever.

100002271.title: Cry Macho
100002271.description: A washed-up rodeo star is hired to retrieve his ex-boss’s troublesome son from Mexico. He bonds with the teen during their arduous trip to the border.

100002273.title: Geostorm
100002273.description: A system of satellites designed to control the climate goes haywire and sets off extreme weather events that threaten to destroy the world.

100002340.title: High Plains Drifter
100002340.description: A gunslinging “Man with No Name” rides into the lawless Western settlement of Lago and makes a name for himself with a string of blazing battles.

100002832.title: Hunting Games
100002832.description: When a group of ex-military members is hired to retrieve a lost bag of stolen money, their mission becomes more difficult after a lone hunter finds the bag first.

100002882.title: The Amazing Spider-Man
100002882.description: Teenage outcast Peter Parker grapples with bullying at his high school and amazing super-human crises as his alter-ego, Spider-Man.

100002883.title: Ghost Rider
100002883.description: Years after superstar motorcycle stunt rider Johnny Blaze made a devil's bargain to protect his loved ones, Beelzebub returns for his due.

100002884.title: Ghost Rider: Spirit of Vengeance
100002884.description: Struggling to repress the Ghost Rider's curse, Johnny Blaze gets a chance at redemption when a secret sect recruits him to protect a boy from Satan.

100002888.description: An academic researcher opens a portal into a parallel universe and makes contact with his double in order to prevent an apocalypse.

100003098.title: Get Close
100003098.description: Tony loses his dad while serving time for a drug offense. When he gets out, he reckons with his grieving family, a vengeful dealer, and his own guilt.

100003156.title: Back to the Future
100003156.description: Marty McFly is blasted to 1955 in a time machine created by Doc Brown and finds himself in a time-shattering situation that jeopardizes his future.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders
0300004985.description: A married veteran Detective Chief Inspector and his young sergeant investigate murders in the quaint, quirky villages of England’s Midsomer County.

0300010320.title: Murder Comes to Town
0300010320.description: Friends and family recount personal stories of horrific crimes that took place in some of the most unassuming places throughout America's heartland.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

0300008167.title: Bad Girls Club
0300008167.description: A group of women with anger and control issues come together and try to improve themselves. But moving forward isn’t going to be easy.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

0300000080.title: The Book of Negroes
0300000080.description: Kidnapped in Africa and enslaved in South Carolina as a girl, a woman attempts to secure her freedom in eighteenth century North America.

0300010082.title: Third Watch
0300010082.description: A drama about the brave and dedicated people who serve as paramedics, firefighters, and police on the “third watch,” the 3:00 PM to 11:00 PM shift.

0300008457.title: The Jeffersons
0300008457.description: Class, race, neighbors, family, and all kinds of clashes make for classic comedy in this beloved series about a family’s move on up to luxury living.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

0300009077.title: The Temptations
0300009077.description: One of Motown's most successful vocal acts was forced to battle prejudice, betrayal, drug abuse and more to become R&B and soul music royalty.

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300000081.title: Hell on Wheels
0300000081.description: An epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who killed his wife.

0300009738.title: Sister, Sister
0300009738.description: Identical twins, separated at birth and adopted by different families, finally meet and try to bring their two very different parents together.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

01077.title: Wildfire
01077.description: Fresh out of juvenile hall, Kris gets a chance at responsibility with a job on a struggling family ranch but soon gets caught up in complicated drama.

04753.title: Beowulf: Return to the Shieldlands
04753.description: In a world of danger populated by both humans and fantastical creatures, Beowulf must slowly reconnect with the notion of family and home.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

0300009178.title: The Dirty D
0300009178.description: Detroit's hottest nightclub is a world of drugs, sex, and money run by a shady power couple. Here there are no rules, and everyone plays for keeps.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

0300006854.title: Scooby-Doo Where Are You?
0300006854.description: The classic adventures of the lovable Great Dane and his human companions as they hunt for clues, hungry for a solution to mysteries and a snack.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.
